is preferred)
5.Secretary (female only,above 170cm,TEM8,GPA3.9)
6.Bodyguard 500(the major function is to fight against the police ,restricte

d only to chinese language and literature,philosophy,history,society.male,un

der 160cm,under 45kg)
7.Cleaner 10  (mainly in charge of restroom cleaning,required IT elites ,the

best of the best)
